This is my first DE map, i hope you like it. This is a apartment that is acually real, which my mom lives in. So what the heck, i made it. Not really the same textures or objects, but you'll get the idea. 

T's start in living room
CT's Start in Bedrooms (2 of em)

Objective: Plant bomb in bathroom

Now watch out, cause the corner to the hallway is were the action takes place (infront of bathroom) 

Theres lots of room in the back of the house, srry if i didnt add those screens

Have Fun!!! :)
